{
  "metadata": {
    "name": "1D KdV equation (u_t + alpha*u*u_x + beta*u_xxx = 0)",
    "description": "Kortewegâ€“de Vries equation in 1D with initial condition u(x,0)=2 sech^2(x-0.5) and periodic boundary conditions on x in [0,1]."
